      <div xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882">
        <head xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Hd1e99" type="question-title">De zelo (in De periculis)</head>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-d1e102">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e112" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Rd1e104">Gregorius, in <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e112">Apud misericordem judicem nequaquam sine venia
              culpa relinquitur, cum per fervorem zeli ex ejus amore peccatur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-d1e117">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e127" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Rd1e119">Gregorius, in <title>Pastorali</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e127">Exasperatus rector, cum subditorum mentem plus
              se quam debuit percussisse considerat apud se, ad poenitentiam semper recurrat, ut per
              lamenta veniam in conspectu veritatis obtineat ex eo etiam, quod per zeli ejus studium
              peccat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-d1e132">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e142" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Rd1e134">Isidorus, <title>de Summo bono</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e142">Nimia pietas dissolutionem disciplinae parturit,
              et zeli studium, dum plus est quam oportet, in iracundiae vitium transit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-d1e147">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e157" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Rd1e149">Bernardus, <title>super Cantica</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e157">Zelus minus absque scientia efficax, minusque
              utile invenitur; plerumque autem et perniciosus valde sentitur. Quo zelus fervidior,
              vehementior spiritus, profusiorque charitas, eo vigilantiori opus est scientia, quae
              zelum supprimat, spiritum temperet, ordinet charitatem.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-d1e163">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e173" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Rd1e165">Bernardus, <title>de Consideratione</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e35882-Qd1e173">Vides omnem ecclesiasticum zelum fervere sola
              pro dignitate tuenda: honoribus totum datur, sanctitati nihil.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
      </div>
